0px 48px 36px;\n  border-radius: 15px;\n  margin: 24px 24px 0;\n  position: relative;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .page-header::before {\n  content: '''';\n  position: absolute;\n  top: -60px;\n  right: -60px;\n  width: 220px;\n  height: 220px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .page-header::after {\n  content: '''';\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: -40px;\n  right: 80px;\n  width: 140px;\n  height: 140px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);\n  pointer-events: none;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .page-header .eyebrow {\n  font-size: 0.72rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 0.14em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .page-header h1 {\n  font-size: 24px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n  color: #fff;\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  border: none;\n  text-transform: none;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .page-header .meta {\n  font-size: 0.78rem;\n  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);\n  margin-top: 14px;\n}\n\n/* CONTAINER */\n.cvs-terms-doc .container {\n  max-width: 760px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 40px 24px 80px;\n}\n\n/* NOTICE */\n.cvs-terms-doc .notice {\n  background: #e6f4f4;\n  border-left: 4px solid #1d8c8c;\n  padding: 16px 20px;\n  margin-bottom: 40px;\n  font-size: 0.875rem;\n  color: #155f5f;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\n}\n\n/* SECTIONS */\n.cvs-terms-doc .container h2 {\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #1d8c8c;\n  margin-top: 40px;\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  padding-bottom: 8px;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #d4e8e8;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .container p {\n  margin-bottom: 16px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: #444;\n  line-height: 1.8;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .container ul {\n  margin: 0 0 16px 0;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: #444;\n  list-style: none;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .container ul li {\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  padding-left: 20px;\n  position: relative;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .container ul li::before {\n  content: '''';\n  position: absolute;\n  left: 0;\n  top: 10px;\n  width: 7px;\n  height: 7px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: #1d8c8c;\n  opacity: 0.6;\n}\n\n/* FOOTER */\n.cvs-terms-doc .footer {\n  margin-top: 60px;\n  padding-top: 24px;\n  border-top: 1px solid #d4e8e8;\n  font-size: 0.78rem;\n  color: #999;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .footer strong {\n  color: #1d8c8c;\n}\n\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .plan-badge {\n  display: inline-block;\n  background: #4a7c59;\n  color: #fff;\n  font-size: 0.65rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  padding: 3px 11px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  margin-left: 10px;\n  vertical-align: middle;\n  position: relative;\n  top: -3px;\n}\n<\/style>\n<\/head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"cvs-terms-doc\">\n<div class=\"page-header\">\n    <div class=\"eyebrow\">Clarity Vision Solutions \u005cu2014 Service Plan<\/div>\n    <h1>Artisan Protection Plan<br><span class=\"plan-badge\">BASIC<\/span>\n    \u005cu2014 Terms &amp; Conditions<\/h1>\n    <div class=\"meta\">Effective Date: January 1, 2026 &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; Version 1.0<\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <div class=\"notice\">\n      Please read these terms carefully before activating your Service Plan. By purchasing or activating the Artisan Protection Plan \u005cu2014 Basic, you agree to be bound by the terms set forth below.\n    <\/div>\n\n    <h2>1. Coverage Overview<\/h2>\n    <p>The Artisan Protection Plan \u005cu2014 Basic provides limited repair and replacement coverage for eligible Clarity Vision Solutions eyewear products purchased through authorized channels. Coverage begins on the date of product purchase and remains active for the duration specified in your plan.<\/p>\n    <p>Coverage Duration: <strong>12 months<\/strong> from the date of purchase.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>2. What Is Covered<\/h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Manufacturing defects in frames and lenses under normal use conditions.<\/li>\n      <li>Accidental damage including scratches, frame breakage, and minor lens damage.<\/li>\n      <li>One (1) covered repair or replacement event per plan term.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n\n    <h2>3. What Is Not Covered<\/h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Loss or theft of the product.<\/li>\n      <li>Damage resulting from misuse, neglect, or unauthorized modifications.<\/li>\n      <li>Cosmetic damage that does not affect the functionality of the eyewear.<\/li>\n      <li>Prescription lens changes due to changes in vision.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n\n    <h2>4. Claims Process<\/h2>\n    <p>To submit a claim, contact Clarity Vision Solutions customer support through your account portal. Claims must be submitted within the active coverage period. A maximum of <strong>two (2) claims<\/strong> may be submitted per plan term. The maximum claim value covered under this plan is <strong>$250.00 USD<\/strong>.<\/p>\n    <p>Clarity reserves the right to repair or replace the covered item at its sole discretion. Replacement products may be of equal or comparable value.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>5. Grace Period<\/h2>\n    <p>A grace period of <strong>30 days<\/strong> applies following the expiration of this plan. Claims submitted during the grace period for damage or defects that occurred during the active coverage term will be honored.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>6. Transferability<\/h2>\n    <p>This plan is non-transferable and applies solely to the original purchaser of the covered product. It may not be assigned, sold, or otherwise transferred to any third party.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>7. Limitation of Liability<\/h2>\n    <p>Clarity Vision Solutions'' total liability under this plan shall not exceed the original purchase price of the covered product. To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, Clarity disclaims all implied warranties, including warran