;\n  padding: 0;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .container ul li {\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  padding-left: 20px;\n  position: relative;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .container ul li::before {\n  content: '''';\n  position: absolute;\n  left: 0;\n  top: 10px;\n  width: 7px;\n  height: 7px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: #1d8c8c;\n  opacity: 0.6;\n}\n\n/* FOOTER */\n.cvs-terms-doc .footer {\n  margin-top: 60px;\n  padding-top: 24px;\n  border-top: 1px solid #d4e8e8;\n  font-size: 0.78rem;\n  color: #999;\n}\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .footer strong {\n  color: #1d8c8c;\n}\n\n\n.cvs-terms-doc .plan-badge {\n  display: inline-block;\n  background: #b5791f;\n  color: #fff;\n  font-size: 0.65rem;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  padding: 3px 11px;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  margin-left: 10px;\n  vertical-align: middle;\n  position: relative;\n  top: -3px;\n}\n<\/style>\n<\/head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"cvs-terms-doc\">\n<div class=\"page-header\">\n    <div class=\"eyebrow\">Clarity Vision Solutions \u005cu2014 Service Plan<\/div>\n    <h1>Artisan Protection Plan<br><span class=\"plan-badge\">PREMIUM<\/span>\n    \u005cu2014 Terms &amp; Conditions<\/h1>\n    <div class=\"meta\">Effective Date: January 1, 2026 &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; Version 1.0<\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n\n    <div class=\"notice\">\n      Please read these terms carefully before activating your Service Plan. By purchasing or activating the Artisan Protection Plan \u005cu2014 Premium, you agree to be bound by the terms set forth below.\n    <\/div>\n\n    <h2>1. Coverage Overview<\/h2>\n    <p>The Artisan Protection Plan \u005cu2014 Premium provides our highest level of repair and replacement coverage for eligible Clarity Vision Solutions eyewear products purchased through authorized channels. Coverage begins on the date of product purchase and remains active for the duration specified in your plan.<\/p>\n    <p>Coverage Duration: <strong>24 months<\/strong> from the date of purchase.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>2. What Is Covered<\/h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Manufacturing defects in frames and lenses under normal use conditions.<\/li>\n      <li>Accidental damage including scratches, frame breakage, lens damage, hinge failure, and coating delamination.<\/li>\n      <li><strong>Unlimited<\/strong> covered repair or replacement events per plan term.<\/li>\n      <li>Standard and premium lens cleaning, adjustment, and realignment services at authorized Clarity service centers.<\/li>\n      <li>Priority processing for all claims and service requests.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n\n    <h2>3. What Is Not Covered<\/h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Loss or theft of the product.<\/li>\n      <li>Intentional damage or damage resulting from gross negligence.<\/li>\n      <li>Prescription lens changes due to changes in vision.<\/li>\n      <li>Damage caused by exposure to extreme heat, chemicals, or corrosive environments beyond normal use.<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n\n    <h2>4. Claims Process<\/h2>\n    <p>To submit a claim, contact Clarity Vision Solutions customer support through your account portal, via our dedicated Premium support line, or visit an authorized service center. Claims must be submitted within the active coverage period. <strong>Unlimited claims<\/strong> may be submitted per plan term. The maximum claim value covered under this plan is <strong>$1,000.00 USD<\/strong> per claim.<\/p>\n    <p>Premium plan holders receive priority claim processing. Clarity reserves the right to repair or replace the covered item. In cases where a direct replacement is not available, a product of equivalent or superior specification will be provided at no additional cost.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>5. Grace Period<\/h2>\n    <p>A grace period of <strong>90 days<\/strong> applies following the expiration of this plan. Claims submitted during the grace period for damage or defects that occurred during the active coverage term will be honored subject to standard review procedures.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>6. Underwriter<\/h2>\n    <p>Coverage under this plan is underwritten by <strong>PrimeGuard Insurance Co.<\/strong>, a licensed insurance provider specializing in consumer product protection. Claims are subject to the underwriter''s review and approval process. Clarity Vision Solutions acts as the plan administrator.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>7. Transferability<\/h2>\n    <p>This plan is non-transferable and applies solely to the original purchaser of the covered product. It may not be assigned, sold, or otherwise transferred to any third party without prior written consent from Clarity Vision Solutions.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>8. Limitation of Liability<\/h2>\n    <p>Clarity Vision Solutions'' and PrimeGuard Insurance Co.''s combined total liability under this plan shall not exceed $1,000.00 USD per claim event. To the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, all implied warranties beyond those expressly stated herein are disclaimed.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>9. Dispute Resolution<\/h2>\n    <p>In the event of a dispute arising from this plan, the parties agree to first attempt resolution through Clarity''s customer support escalation process. Unresolved disputes shall be subject to binding arbitration under the rules of the American Arbitration Association.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>10. Governing Law<\/h2>\n    <p>These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of California, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.<\/p>\n\n    <h2>11. Amendments<\/h2>\n    <p>Clarity Vision Solutions reserves the right to amend these terms at any time with reasonable notice. Continued use of the plan following notice of changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.<\/p>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n      &copy; 2026 Clarity Vision Solutions. All rights reserved. &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; For questions, contact <strong>support@clarityvisionsolutions.com<\/strong> or call our Premium support line.\n    <\/div>\n\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/body>\n<\/html>","config":{}}}}','lddo',0,'BASIC_COMPONENT-html',1,'2026-06-19 22:50:37.305000',NULL)
